title: Samurai Warriors 2 Empires
description:
Samurai Warriors 2: Empires. I spent a lot of time playing this game with my brother 

as a kid. Create your own warrior and test his mettle in battle as you try to unite 

all of Japan! The game plays like Samurai Warriors 2 but includes that same tactical 

element that the other empire games brought to Koei titles, employ officers, hire 

troops, and perform stratagems. Hope you like it as much as I do!




-Sershadak
